== GIT CLONE gnuradio repo ==
<pre>
mkdir ~/sandbox
cd ~/sandbox
git clone https://github.com/gnuradio/gnuradio.git ./gnuradio
</pre>

== checkout version v3.7.1 release ==
<pre>
cd gnuradio
git checkout tags/v3.7.1
</pre>

== build GNURadio ==
<pre>
mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/opt/gnuradio-3.7.1 ../
make -j4
sudo make install
</pre>